</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The Dow Jones industrial average is up 29.45 to  
10,817.25 just before 3 p.m. EDT, after being up more than 100 
earlier today. Market breadth is just slightly positive with 1,505 
advancers and 1,454 decliners on the New York Stock Exchange. The 
Nasdaq Composite Index is down 6.40 to 2,558.58. 

</P>
