</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Blue-chip stocks were held to a minuscule gain  
and broader indicators retreated today after interest rates surged 
following a disappointing Treasury bond auction. The Dow Jones 
industrials ended up 1.59 at 10,789.39. Declines led advancers on 
the New York Stock Exchange 1,525-1,490. The Nasdaq Composite Index 
was down 15.50 at 2,549.48. 

