<HEADLINE> Cavaliers Sign Mark Bryant </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CLEVELAND (AP) -- The Cleveland Cavaliers added depth to their  
front court today by signing free agent forward Mark Bryant to a 
two-year deal. 
</P>
<P>
	Bryant, an 11-year NBA veteran, spent the 1998-99 season with  
