 *Clorox, down 16 11/16 at 86 9/16    	
</P>
<P>
	Clorox earned 42 cents per share in its fiscal fourth-quarter,  
down from 91 cents per share in the same period last year, as it 
took a charge for the acquisition of First Brands. Lower sales of 
