	San Jose tied it in the 54th minute, thanks to an own goal by  
Causey, playing for injured Walter Zenga. 
</P>
<P>
	The goal came when Jeff Baicher's corner kick was headed toward  
the right post by John Doyle. Causey made an awkward save and 
accidentally kicked the ball into his net. 
  	   	
