<HEADLINE> British Stocks End Higher / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices rose Thursday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was up 138.9  
points, or 2.3 percent, at 6,153.3. 
</P>
